OL,3,CMan confronted by male armed with
OL,4,Cknives in Ballymena burglary
OL,6,FA man in his 60s has been confronted
OL,7,Fby a male armed with two knives during
OL,8,Fa burglary at a house in Ballymena.
OL,10,FPolice received reports that a man
OL,11,Fdressed in dark clothing with his face
OL,12,Fcovered entered the property in the
OL,13,FFrancis Street area shortly before 8am
OL,14,Fon Thursday 21 May .
OL,16,FThe armed male confronted a man in his
OL,17,F60s who was inside the property before
OL,18,Fmaking off in the direction of Larne
OL,19,FRoad on an e-scooter.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
