OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779700299
OL,3,CMan confronted by male armed with
OL,4,Cknives in Ballymena burglary
OL,6,FNo one was injured but a number of
OL,7,Fitems were taken.
OL,9,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "At around
OL,10,F7:50am, it was reported that a man
OL,11,Fdressed in dark coloured clothing
OL,12,Fentered the property with his face
OL,13,Fcovered.
OL,15,F"The male, who was armed with two
OL,16,Fknives, confronted a man in his 60s
OL,17,Fwho was inside the property.
OL,26,@qD@[OU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
