PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1779700299
OL,3,CMan confronted by male armed with
OL,4,Cknives in Ballymena burglary
OL,6,F"The male then made off, dropping one
OL,7,Fof the knives, towards the Larne Road
OL,8,Farea on an e-scooter following the
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,F"The male occupant was not injured,
OL,12,Fbut a wallet containing bank cards and
OL,13,Fcash as well as a necklace were taken
OL,14,Fduring the incident."
OL,16,FEnquiries are continuing and police
OL,17,Fhave appealed to anyone with any
OL,18,Finformation or footage taken at the
OL,19,Ftime to contact them.
